Benar, bukan, Da Bin?

754
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:46,320
Benar.

755
00:41:46,959 --> 00:41:49,529
Kenapa? Kenapa kamu melakukan itu?

756
00:41:50,060 --> 00:41:51,190
Kenapa lagi?

757
00:41:51,289 --> 00:41:55,060
Agar kamu mengembalikan sepedaku.

758
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:56,930
Astaga, bukan main.

759
00:41:57,729 --> 00:42:00,700
Baik. Karena sudah memakai celemek,

760
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:02,599
kamu bisa sekalian mencuci baju

761
